Nothing. I'm just saying

14:18.107 --> 14:19.818
I don't have the string.

14:19.859 --> 14:21.110
You're the last person

14:19.859 --> 14:21.110
I saw it with.

14:21.152 --> 14:22.903
What the hell are

14:21.152 --> 14:22.903
we going to do

14:22.945 --> 14:23.904
without that string?

14:23.946 --> 14:26.741
Guys, come on.

14:23.946 --> 14:26.741
It's just a stupid string.

14:29.160 --> 14:30.911
So what do you think

14:29.160 --> 14:30.911
would be a reason

14:30.953 --> 14:31.912
for saying that, Eric?

14:31.954 --> 14:32.955
You're the only one

14:32.997 --> 14:34.915
who seems to have a motive

14:32.997 --> 14:34.915
against the string.

14:34.957 --> 14:36.917
No, I love the string.

14:34.957 --> 14:36.917
It's just...

14:36.959 --> 14:38.712
Maybe you loved it

14:36.959 --> 14:38.712
a little too much.

14:38.753 --> 14:40.171
And I quote,

14:40.213 --> 14:43.424
"If I can't have

14:40.213 --> 14:43.424
the string, no one will."

14:43.466 --> 14:44.634
I didn't say that!

14:44.676 --> 14:45.510
Well, someone said it!

14:45.552 --> 14:46.927
You just now!

14:46.969 --> 14:48.722
Don't try to twist

14:46.969 --> 14:48.722
this around.

14:48.763 --> 14:49.930
He's not the one

14:48.763 --> 14:49.930
on trial.

14:49.972 --> 14:51.932
What trial?!

14:51.974 --> 14:54.060
Guilty!

15:13.580 --> 15:15.164
He raises four.

15:15.206 --> 15:17.958
Your four,

15:15.206 --> 15:17.958
five more.

15:18.000 --> 15:19.252
Malcolm, maybe...

15:19.293 --> 15:21.337
You want to play?

15:19.293 --> 15:21.337
Fine.

15:21.379 --> 15:23.548
I almost feel

15:21.379 --> 15:23.548
sorry for them.

15:23.590 --> 15:24.549
Almost.

15:24.591 --> 15:25.759
(laughs)

15:25.800 --> 15:28.762
All right, we're going

15:25.800 --> 15:28.762
to end this right here.

15:28.803 --> 15:29.763
Winner take all.

15:29.804 --> 15:31.972
Fine.

15:32.014 --> 15:32.807
Turn 'em up.

15:32.849 --> 15:33.974
Three fives.

15:34.016 --> 15:35.894
Three fives with a jack.

15:35.935 --> 15:37.645
Yeah!

15:39.021 --> 15:41.482
That makes six fives!

15:41.524 --> 15:44.193
What the hell kind

15:41.524 --> 15:44.193
of deck has six fives!

15:44.235 --> 15:45.986
I don't know.

15:44.235 --> 15:45.986
I got 'em from the boys' room.

15:46.028 --> 15:47.154
You call yourself

15:46.028 --> 15:47.154
