15:47.196 --> 15:48.865
You don't even have

15:47.196 --> 15:48.865
a decent deck.

15:48.907 --> 15:49.866
Well, I'm sorry

15:49.908 --> 15:51.409
I don't have

15:49.908 --> 15:51.409
solid gold playing cards

15:51.451 --> 15:53.453
like you're accustomed to

15:51.451 --> 15:53.453
at your house.

15:53.494 --> 15:55.996
This poor-guy act is

15:53.494 --> 15:55.996
getting a little tiring!

15:56.038 --> 15:58.708
Your superior act

15:56.038 --> 15:58.708
