15:58.750 --> 16:01.001
If I'm such a big jerk

15:58.750 --> 16:01.001
why'd you even come over?!

16:01.043 --> 16:03.003
Pardon me for wanting

16:01.043 --> 16:03.003
to play poker

16:03.045 --> 16:05.214
with my best friend!

16:09.844 --> 16:14.014
I mean, I was really excited

16:09.844 --> 16:14.014
to come over and play poker

16:14.056 --> 16:16.893
and meet your other friends.

16:18.978 --> 16:24.275
Truth be told, I was excited

16:18.978 --> 16:24.275
