16:24.317 --> 16:26.653
I bought a new shirt.

16:26.694 --> 16:27.862
That Hawaiian one?

16:28.696 --> 16:31.157
I like that one.

16:33.075 --> 16:35.035
Why are we fighting

16:33.075 --> 16:35.035
like this?

16:35.077 --> 16:37.538
Because we're idiots!

16:37.580 --> 16:39.874
(both laugh)

16:42.919 --> 16:45.546
(both laugh)

16:47.089 --> 16:49.091
Well, boys, what do you say

16:47.089 --> 16:49.091
we all go out

16:49.133 --> 16:50.551
to get some ice cream?

16:50.593 --> 16:51.845
Sounds good to me.

16:51.886 --> 16:55.222
Hey, Dewey, come on.

16:51.886 --> 16:55.222
We're going for ice cream.

16:55.264 --> 16:56.975
Where's your brother?

