As for the rest of you,

17:00.603 --> 17:03.523
I'm not running a charity here.

17:03.564 --> 17:05.733
You have to come up

17:03.564 --> 17:05.733
with the dough!

17:05.775 --> 17:07.861
I do not dance on credit.

17:07.902 --> 17:09.362
No offense, but some of you

17:09.403 --> 17:12.281
might not even be around

17:09.403 --> 17:12.281
