18:10.172 --> 18:12.884
Lois, Lois, please.

18:10.172 --> 18:12.884
Come-come with me.

18:17.179 --> 18:18.138
Uh...

18:18.180 --> 18:20.433
We have to stop this.

18:20.474 --> 18:21.308
Why?

18:21.350 --> 18:23.143
Honey, you've outgrown me.

